== Caaqibada Shirkiga ==
Caaqibada shirkiga laga dhaxlo ayaa ah in la buriyo wax walboo camal ah oo aad hormarsatay iyo markaas aad wadidba, aakhirana wuxuu galayaa qofkii sameeya naarta,<ref>http://towhed.com/index.php/maktaba/11-2013-12-31-05-32-53/38-2014-01-09-20-18-14{{Dead link|date=August 2021 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 

ilaahay wuxuu yiri asagoo nabigiisa la hadlaya hadaad shirki samayso waxaa buray camalkaaga oo dhan aakhirana waad khasaaraysaa  ﴿وَلَوْ أَشْرَكُوا  لَحَبِطَ عَنْهُمْ مَّا كَانُوا يَعْمَلُونَ﴾  [الأنعام: 88<ref>http://quran.ksu.edu.sa/tafseer/tabary/sura5-aya72.html</ref>]

